column4: Tesla meets fourth-quarter estimate with 17 400 vehicles delivered
column5: Tesla Motors Inc   the pioneering electric car maker  said on Sunday it delivered 17 400 vehicles during the fourth quarter of 2015  in line with its forecasts  and a total of 50 580 for the year.
